Clinton, IA (52732)

Today

Scattered thunderstorms during the morning. Partly cloudy skies this afternoon. High 87F. Winds SSW at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 50%..

Tonight

Variable clouds with thunderstorms, especially late. Low 67F. Winds SE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 40%.
